Flub.Name: Rough
Flub.Description: Adds localized sharpness and protrusions based on the local shape of the terrain.

Flub.Name: Rocky
Flub.Description: Creates lots of tiny rocks based on the local shape of the terrain.

Flub.Name: Coverage
Flub.Description: Coverage across larger features. Low values localize the effect, while high values let it spread across larger shapes.

Flub.Name: Density
Flub.Description: Density of rock protrusions created on the surface.
